\par }{\b\f0\fs32\lang2057\langfe1055\langnp2057\insrsid4216250\charrsid881378 The Superior Morality of the Prophet Musa (as)
\par }{\f0\fs22\lang2057\langfe1055\langnp2057\insrsid4216250\charrsid881378 
\par The Qur'an pro
vides a detailed account of the Prophet Musa's struggle with the Pharaoh, a man who has gone down as one of the most oppressive rulers in history. The Pharaoh responded to message of God communicated to him by the Prophet Musa (as) with threats and abuse.
